(8, 1, '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '<h2 class="category-title">INDUSTRIES</h2>\n<p>At The Anorga Law Firm, our  client industries include:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Hospitality – Restaurants, Bars, Hotels and Motels</li>\n  <li>Doctors and Licensed Professionals</li>\n  <li>Medical Providers</li>\n  <li>Commercial Real Estate</li>\n  <li>Residential Real Estate</li>\n  <li>Manufacturing and Distribution</li>\n  <li>Clothing</li>\n  <li>Marketing</li>\n  <li>Insurance</li>\n  <li>Entertainment – Studios, Musicians, Producers,  Directors and All Talent</li>\n  <li>Technology</li>\n</ul>', 'INDUSTRIES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'industries', '', '', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '', 0, 'http://edbangoy.com/law/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '\n\n', 'MEDIA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'media', '', '', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '', 0, 'http://edbangoy.com/law/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '<h2 class="category-title">TESTIMONIALS</h2>\n<p>[quote type="center"] Omar Anorga has been providing legal services to my medical practice since September 2008. In baseball terms, he is batting a 1000! He has always delivered good results for me for every problem I\'ve had. Even though I\'m a self-employed physician, my medical practice at the end of the day is a small business. It is not uncommon for small business\' to encounter unforeseen challenges, such as labor issues, threatening litigation. Mr. Anorga has always "quelled" every problem my small business has encountered. I strongly recommend Mr. Anorga to handle your small business problems and general litigation matters.</p>\n\n<p>- Dr. Victor Carabello[/quote]</p>\n<p>[quote type="center"] Omar  Anorga’s passion and dedication is what differentiates him from other attorneys  in the industry. Omar develops sound legal strategies to give his clients the  greatest opportunity for success while limiting their financial exposure. Not  only does he fearlessly represent his clients but he also gives tremendous  amounts of his time educating his clients on the legal process to ensure his  clients are well informed and comfortable with the legal direction they are  embarking on.</p>\n\n<p>- T. Chukuka[/quote]</p>\n<p>[quote type="center"] The Anorga Law Firm has been a tremendous  help in the growth of our business. The firm\'s professionalism and knowledge of  small business-entrepreneurship matters&nbsp;has been extremely valuable. The  rates are more than affordable and they always give us the time and attention  we need. </p>\n\n<p>- Forte- The Collective[/quote]</p>\n<p>[quote type="center"] Our family business was given a positive  referral to Mr. Anorga as we wanted to pursue Downtown L.A. representation for  our commercial properties. We have found Mr. Anorga very responsive,  knowledgeable and excellent to work with.</p>\n\n<p>- John K., from JK/MK #3 Properties,  LLC.[/quote]</p>\n<p>[quote type="center"] I have had the pleasure of working with  attorney Omar Anorga recently on a civil litigation dispute. I was highly  impressed with his professionalism and attention to detail, as well as his  knowledge of the law and facts of the case. I recommend Mr. Anorga to anyone  looking for exceptional legal representation.</p>\n\n<p>-Moses A. Yneges, Esq. [/quote] </p>\n', 'TESTIMONIALS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'testimonials', '', '', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '', 0, 'http://edbangoy.com/law/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '2013-03-22 11:49:52', '\r\n<h2 class="category-title">CONTACT US</h2>\r\n<p>The Anorga Law Firm, Inc.<br /> 155 North Lake Avenue, Suite 800<br /> Pasadena, CA 91101</p>\r\n<p><iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m16!1m10!1m3!1d3301.9150777613822!2d-118.1324034984751!3d34.14851470711083!2m1!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x80c2c342e26595bd%3A0x5326b54bb6ab70d2!2s155+N+Lake+Ave+%23800%2C+Pasadena%2C+CA+91101!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1415207107983" width="425" height="350" frameborder="0" style="border:0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>Phone:            213 489-1271<br /> Fax:                 213 223-6811<br /> Email:             <a href="mailto:info@anorgalaw.com">info@anorgalaw.com</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Anorga-Law-Firm-Inc/282743561855543?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts" target="_blank"><img style="margin-right: 8px;" alt="Facebook" src="http://edbangoy.com/law/wp-content/themes/Law/images/facebook.png" /></a><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=19788223" target="_blank"><img style="margin-right: 8px;" alt="Rss" src="http://edbangoy.com/law/wp-content/themes/Law/images/rss.png" /></a><a href="https://twitter.com/AnorgaLaw" target="_blank"><img alt="Twitter" src="http://edbangoy.com/law/wp-content/themes/Law/images/twitter.png" /></a></p>\r\n', 'CONTACT', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'contact', '', '', '2014-11-05 17:07:52', '2014-11-05 17:07:52', '', 0, 'http://edbangoy.com/law/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
