(54, 1, '2013-03-22 13:03:48', '2013-03-22 13:03:48', '<h2 class="category-title" id="FRANCHISE">FRANCHISE</h2>\n<p>  The Anorga Law Firm’s  practice includes franchise, which is a business relationship between a  franchisor, a party that grants a franchise, and a franchisee, the party to  whom the franchise is granted, under which the franchisee is allowed to conduct  business offering goods or services to others. The Anorga Law Firm counsels both franchisors and franchisees and assists in the establishment of, and becoming a part of, franchise systems. </p>', 'FRANCHISE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'franchise', '', '', '2013-03-22 13:03:48', '2013-03-22 13:03:48', '', 0, 'http://edbangoy.com/law/franchise/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(57, 2, '2011-04-08 16:38:01', '2011-04-08 23:38:01', 'I know it\'s been awhile since I last blogged, but I wanted to quickly post something about the California Hispanic Corporate Council Institute.\n\nI was invited to attend one of its events last night at the City Club in Downtown Los Angeles.\n\nThe speaker for the evening was Gaddi Vasquez, the first Latino Director for the Peace Corps, and former U.S. Ambassador.  It was a delight to hear Mr. Vasquez talk about his experiences throughout life\n\nI will be attending more events for the California Hispanic Corporate Council Institute.  Maybe you would like to, too.\n\nStay for more blogging starting next week.\n\nThanks!', 'The California Hispanic Corporate Council Institute ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-california-hispanic-corporate-council-institute', '', '', '2014-11-05 17:51:18', '2014-11-05 17:51:18', '', 0, 'http://anorgalaw.com/blog/?p=57', 0, 'post', '', 0),
