(171, 1, '2013-04-13 12:34:10', '2013-04-13 12:34:10', '\n<p><strong>Los Angeles, CA</strong> (January 4, 2010) – The Los Angeles Business Journal in conjunction with the Latino Business Chamber of Greater Los Angeles and Comerica Bank, announced the nomination of <strong>The Law Office of Omar S. Anorga</strong> for the <strong>2010 Latino Business Award</strong>. The event will recognize outstanding Latino businesses that are leading the charge for excellence within the Los Angeles business community. Setting a perfect example is The Law Office of Omar S. Anorga, a litigation law firm based in the heart of downtown.<br /> <br /><a href="http://anorgalaw.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/prl1.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-47" alt="prl" src="http://anorgalaw.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/prl1.png" width="139" height="167" /></a> “As a native Los Angelino born and raised in the area, I am incredibly proud and honored to be among the nominees for this award,” says Omar S. Anorga, the owner and founder of the law firm. “It’s a privilege and honor to be part of this neighborhood where I grew up and can give back as a Latino minority business owner. I am grateful for the nomination.”<br /> <br /> The Law Office of Omar S. Anorga is dedicated to providing personal attention, counseling and guidance to the Los Angeles business community, particularly the Latino-owned and minority-owned businesses. Their goal is to provide smart, innovative and relentless legal representation to their clients. Although a full-service law firm, they concentrate on three key areas: Business Law, Real Estate Law and Employment Law.<br /> <br /> The winners of The Latino Business Awards will be announced at the event luncheon scheduled to take place on Wednesday, January 20 at the Millennium Biltmore Hotel in downtown L.A. where several hundred guests are expected to attend. There are four categories for the awards which include: public company, small private company, large private company and non-profit organization. A special edition announcing the winners will be revealed in the January 25 publication of the Los Angeles Business Journal.</p>\n', 'LA Business Journal Announces Anorga', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '46-autosave', '', '', '2013-04-13 12:34:10', '2013-04-13 12:34:10', '', 46, 'http://anorgalaw.com/46-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
