pany, small private company, large  private company and non-profit organization. A special edition  announcing the winners will be revealed in the January 25 publication  of the Los Angeles Business Journal.</p>', 'LA Business Journal Announces Anorga', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '46-revision', '', '', '2013-03-22 12:48:42', '2013-03-22 12:48:42', '', 46, 'http://anorgalaw.com/46-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
