ate company and non-profit organization. A special edition announcing the winners will be revealed in the January 25 publication of the Los Angeles Business Journal.</p>\r\n', 'LA Business Journal Announces Anorga', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '46-revision-2', '', '', '2013-04-13 06:37:11', '2013-04-13 06:37:11', '', 46, 'http://anorgalaw.com/46-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
